description:
This is a 62 minute workout called '60 Minute Indoor Cycling Workout | Endurance Ride' from the channel RI:ID.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Advanced and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Advanced.
The effort required is Extreme and Challenging.

Original workout description: Join Paul on an epic 60 minute ride, this journey will incorporate two focussed blocks of intensity and a strong finish! This longer adventure will improve your fitness, your strength and burn lot's of calories - ENJOY THE RI:ID
